    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six. This example retains its factory-spec sequential forced induction system, providing a smooth torque curve and minimal turbo lag. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-equipped Torsen limited-slip differential. The vehicle features a well-maintained cooling stack and has recently undergone a comprehensive valve cover gasket replacement and timing belt service to ensure vacuum integrity and mechanical timing precision. The suspension utilizes OEM-plus components for maintaining original geometry while sharpening lateral transitions. Showing honest cosmetic patina consistent with its 'good' status, this A80 remains structurally sound and functionally superior for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
