      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that balances daily utility with pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well. The alloy wheels are in excellent shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather upholstery is supple, showing only light characteristic creasing on the driver\u2019s outer bolster. All electronic features, including the infotainment system, climate control, and heated seats, operate perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in top form. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule, with a major service recently completed that included new brake pads and a fresh fluid flush. The engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It comes with a complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, two key fobs, and a detailed service log. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next chapter.",
